---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us">
  
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative py-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-600 via-winter-600 to-primary-700 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <div class="absolute -top-40 -right-40 w-80 h-80 bg-white/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
      <div class="absolute -bottom-40 -left-40 w-80 h-80 bg-white/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="relative container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-6">
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-white">
          About The Blizzard Wizard
        </h1>
        <p class="text-2xl text-white/90 italic">
          Making Snow Disappear Like Magic Since Day One ‚ú®
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!--Our Story -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-12">
          <div class="lg:col-span-3 space-y-6">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">Our Story</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              The Blizzard Wizard was born from a simple observation: homeowners in the Greater Toronto Area needed a snow removal service they could truly rely on. Not just a company that shows up when it's convenient, but one that understands that winter waits for no one.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              We started with a single plow truck and a commitment to excellence. Today, we serve thousands of residential properties across North York, Richmond Hill, Markham, Vaughan, and Scarborough. Our growth hasn't changed our core mission: to provide exceptional, reliable snow removal service that lets homeowners enjoy winter without worry.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              What makes us different? We focus exclusively on residential properties. This specialization means we understand the unique challenges homeowners face, from protecting landscaping to accommodating different driveway configurations. We're not trying to be everything to everyone ‚Äì we're masters of residential snow removal.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="lg:col-span-2">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-600 via-winter-600 to-primary-700 rounded-3xl p-8 text-white shadow-2xl sticky top-24">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Our Mission</h3>
              <p class="leading-relaxed">
                To provide the most reliable, professional, and customer-focused residential snow removal service in the Greater Toronto Area, ensuring every homeowner can safely access their property throughout winter.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 mb-16">Our Values</h2>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-lg text-center transform hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-500 to-winter-500 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
            <span class="text-4xl">üéØ</span>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Reliability</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            When we say we'll be there, we'll be there. Our customers count on us, and we take that responsibility seriously.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-lg text-center transform hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-winter-500 to-primary-500 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
            <span class="text-4xl">‚≠ê</span>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Quality</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            We don't just push snow around ‚Äì we do the job right. Quality is in every detail of our service.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-lg text-center transform hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-500 to-winter-500 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
            <span class="text-4xl">‚ù§Ô∏è</span>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Care</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Every property is someone's home. We treat your property with the same care we'd want for our own.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-lg text-center transform hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-winter-500 to-primary-500 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
            <span class="text-4xl">üí°</span>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Innovation</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            We continuously improve our equipment and techniques to provide better results for our customers.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Choose Us -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 mb-16">Why Choose Us?</h2>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        {[
          { title: "Residential Specialists", text: "Unlike companies that split focus, we specialize exclusively in homes for better results." },
          { title: "Professional Equipment", text: "Quality equipment specifically chosen for residential properties." },
          { title: "Trained Team", text: "Every member is trained in proper techniques and customer service." },
          { title: "Fully Insured", text: "Comprehensive insurance coverage protects both you and us." },
          { title: "Fair Pricing", text: "Transparent pricing with no hidden fees and flexible payment options." },
          { title: "Local Service", text: "We're part of the communities we serve, not a distant call center." }
        ].map((item) => (
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-4 p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">{item.title}</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">{item.text}</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-600 via-winter-600 to-primary-700">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Experience the Blizzard Wizard Difference</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-white/90 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Join thousands of satisfied homeowners across the GTA who trust us to keep their properties clear all winter long.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-block px-10 py-4 bg-white text-primary-700 font-bold rounded-full text-lg shadow-2xl hover:shadow-3xl transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300">
        Get Your Free Quote Today
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
